dct_title_s: Europe and the Mediterranean : showing communications and political boundaries
dct_description_sm: John Bartholomew & Son Ltd. North Decimal Degree 65.884167. South Decimal Degree 29.250000. East Decimal Degree 52.506944. West Decimal Degree -10.620556. Alternate title:: Bartholomew's map of Europe and the Mediterranean showing communications and political boundaries, 1925. Insets: Bay of Naples; Ahtens and environments, The Bosporus, Malta, Gibraltar, Menton-Monaco-Nice. Map shows broadcasting stations. Palestine is shown on map. Map no.: 461.
